                <h1>From a zoo to an organ: David Rubenstein&#039;s name is everywhere in DC too</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/9f98d4a1-221f-4fc7-8c7c-2594f198626b.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;David&#x20;Rubenstein,&#x20;former&#x20;chair&#x20;of&#x20;the&#x20;Board&#x20;of&#x20;Trustees,&#x20;speaking&#x20;at&#x20;Commencement&#x20;in&#x20;2017.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>David Rubenstein, former chair of the Board of Trustees, speaking at Commencement in 2017.</p>

                                                             <aside class="photo-caption photo-credit d-block pl-1">
                                    <figcaption class="d-block">
